descriptionHtml:
The application provides the opportunity for different professions to communicate with business owners who need to serve these, and the profession (from different professions) can identify himself in his own page, and simply search for a specific service shows the names of all workers in this specialty, as it appears on the page of each person The type of service and evaluation of others and his comments, and also displays the prices charged and address and place on the map.
The application saves a lot of time for all job seekers in various fields, instead of searching the internet, find what it needs in one place, as the umaass saves the professionals a lot of time and effort, as they often have to go and Gathering in known places and there are flocking to anyone who comes to seek service, while the application facilitates the process of communication between the parties.
Professionals are presented for their work history, people's opinion of what they have done in the past and their evaluation of it
The spread of umaass among people creates a wonderful environment through the ease of communication between professionals and those interested in a particular service.
The application does not impose any conditions on the user unless complaints have been received from the service providers.
For service providers, the application does not interfere in any aspect of their work, good evaluation brings more customers and low evaluation contributes to reduce the appetite of others for its services, and in case of negative feedback, the management of the application will take the necessary measures against him Up to unsubscribe .
Variations in the privacy policy and terms and conditions may occur in the future.
